<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-08-0079 </DOCNO><TEXT>The radiograph itself plays a major role in medical malpractice cases.Also, many questions arise concerning the rights to and storage of x-rayfilms. These issues are addressed in this chapter. To keep the terminologysimple, the word radiograph represents all imaging documentation on hardcopy film (x-rays, nuclear medicine, computer-assisted studies, ultrasound,and magnetic resonance imaging).</TEXT></DOC>